The slug provider chain is pluggable: the function runtime queries each registered provider until one returns a slug. The default provider reads from Azure Table Storage, which is refreshed from the Microsoft Cloud Adoption Framework abbreviation table plus local overrides, but additional providers can be added ahead of it to pull slugs from internal services or caches.
